X_{f\circ L_{h^{-1}}} = {L_h}_* X_f
 (L_h^* \pi) (df, dg) = \pi(L_{h^{-1}}^* df, L_{h^{-1}}^* dg) = \pi( d(f\circ L_{h^{-1}}), d(g\circ L_{h^{-1}})) = \omega(X_{f\circ L_{h^{-1}}}, X_{f\circ L_{h^{-1}}}). 
